Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:18.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的羽翼 已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:26.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔时的记忆 却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:37.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你寻回 是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:45.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不随时间的浊流 被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:53.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出些许回忆 始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:01.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留下的些许眼泪 却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:08.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的泪滴 也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:16.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间黑夜被撕裂 光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:23.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁净如洗的太阳 温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:29.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:40.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描绘出的梦之画卷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:49.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去轻轻触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:55.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伸出的指尖 它淡淡消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:02.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 真实的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:12.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 聆听这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:21.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份满溢的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:32.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能传达给最重视的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:48.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(800,0)}{\blur3}伊亚尔和艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使伤及自我也要使用斗蛇这种武力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来保卫辽扎神王国的勇猛的大公
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与能够吃掉斗蛇熠熠生辉的王兽的操控者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时又是国民心中所信仰的圣洁真王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得大公领民和真王领民之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生了扭曲的黑暗漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还想要把一位少女卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉扎鲁王兽保护场把受伤的王兽送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这车子还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大我还是第一次见到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这是为了保全大义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也是个大麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去王兽舍里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚并未发生异样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上过来一看 它就显得十分疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子衰弱了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 这是昨天送过来的王兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先让我看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爪子上的伤并没有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为下巴是张开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以并不像是发了病的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动弹不得而且非常衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是吃了什么不洁的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的呼气中有一股甜甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道的确是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只生长在大公领内地带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常珍贵的野草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么王兽会吃下那种野草…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到过有人吃下参入父拟草的草饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 在一个叫做雾之市的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇见了雾之民 得到解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜这里不是大公领 是真王领
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找到雾之民…很难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王都的药铺 应该会有很多国内药草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那里也许能弄到解毒的药
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这头王兽真的中了父拟草的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕挺不过三天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…也许是两天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 到后天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要找到解毒的药并把它带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这段时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽可能将它体内的毒排出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰的照看就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南 把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公近来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于一时疲劳过度 受病魔侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经缓解下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您操心 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需拔刀 伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关你所追踪的偷蛋贼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查到了你意想不到的关联事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意想不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照规定只有斗蛇众才能去取斗蛇蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一群人专门把蛋运来真王领
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运来真王领?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真王领的中介商的屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人看到一个你所说的假面男子从那里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面那帮人果然是想猎杀真王陛下的血秽族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话 那他们要取斗蛇蛋做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟弥亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责试毒的奈美大人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美 奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我 我是瑟弥亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据宫中的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她吃了一口送给瑟弥亚公主的点心后突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的 花芯的香味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生长在我们大公领的野草 有毒的野草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在我们城内也发生过这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敬奉真王陛下的贡品中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什么人 将父拟草混入了其中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血秽族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血秽族一直都想要刺杀真王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的就是要让大公成为国家之首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你看来会认为这是我或者父亲的阴谋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我坦白的话是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 血秽族应该是不会做让大公丢脸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得一定是有人假冒血秽族暗中作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目标都是真王陛下和瑟弥亚公主的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南 我求求你 救救奈美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟弥亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南大人对地形不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我等坚盾协助他去找寻解药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托你了 伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草的解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草是大公领的毒草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的药铺好像都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许在较城市偏远一点的药铺会有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 什么都不起效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 恐怕挺不到明天早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 希望你能快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是坚盾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来寻找解毒药的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让他们给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就起来赶路 搞得好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 鲁库
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你再坚持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 放心交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受小姑娘所托 我鲁库
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会努力不犯困的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直都在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少在这里逞威风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡了一下下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父拟草是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的话 有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括解毒药在内全部给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您稍等一下 我核对一下在库数目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 我是坚盾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是来做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来买父拟草的解毒药…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认错人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你遭灾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把艾琳给忘记了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要找的药是叫做风铃草的根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在这副惨状上哪儿去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就在这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看起来每种草都一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 风铃草是这两种的哪一种?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这种 亏你还能分出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两种的味道都很像解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要找这个草药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽中毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从拉扎鲁送来治疗的王兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是在哪儿中毒的 我们还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒…包下解毒药的假面男…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让那只王兽死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个毒一定是让什么人灌入体内的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时那个人不想让你们拿到解药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就这样回去会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我们赶紧回去送解药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一定要送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你们走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要给我从实招来 血秽族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经断气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是用毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么坚盾的你会跟着来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽是真王陛下的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让世人知道王兽被毒杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会产生各种各样的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真王陛下的权威会受到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了这个才去给王兽下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说也许就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对这个国家来说可是头等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们坚盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了守护真王陛下而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们为什么要为了自己的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要把动物也牵扯进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物并不是为了人类而生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很重视王兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想它死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面这座桥倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马车是通不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有返回王都绕路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的话就会来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单是人通过的话 前面倒有座吊桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿明明有个鸟巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鸟儿却回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧回卡扎姆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来记得我名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被人知道你和坚盾扯上关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我装作不认识你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解药找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只王兽呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了艾沙鲁老师把毒吸了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算还挺得住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是坚盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去王兽那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔先生 真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个教导师好像在哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下应该不会有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真王陛下 瑟弥亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们为我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像恢复过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳和伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过两人的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了发生在王宫和卡扎姆的中毒事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐蚀这个国家的毒还在静静的蔓延中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.88,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 你要好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:09.39,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀受了伤送来卡扎姆治疗的野生王兽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:11.24,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫做艾克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.38,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是雄性的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.54,0:24:15.27,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰喜不喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:18.56,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等艾克的伤好了 恢复健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:20.37,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰就和它一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.61,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:24.59,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:30.21,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,255)}新的生命


